{"word":"H393 - אַכְזָר - ʼakzâr - ak-zawr' - Cruel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אַכְזָר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼakzâr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ak-zawr'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cruel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கொடிய, கொடூரமுள்ள, குரூரமுள்ள, தைரியமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"cruel, fierce"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From an unused root (apparently meaning to <i>act harshly</i>); <i>violent</i>; by implication <i>deadly</i>; also (in a good sense) <i>brave: - </i>cruel, fierce."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3581 - כֹּחַ - kôach - ko'-akh/3581\">H3581</a>, <a href=\"#/H393 - אַכְזָר - ʼakzâr - ak-zawr'/393\">H393</a>, <a href=\"#/H394 - אַכְזָרִי - ʼakzârîy - ak-zawr-ree'/394\">H394</a>, <a href=\"#/H395 - אַכְזְרִיּוּת - ʼakzᵉrîyûwth - ak-ze-ree-ooth'/395\">H395</a>"}]}